name: Savanna project
body:
### Welcome to the Savanna project's site.

Our site has been moved to the [savanna.readthedocs.org](https://savanna.readthedocs.org).

You will be redirected momentarily...

### Versioning

Now you can easily access any version of the site using features of the readthedocs.org.

For example:

* Savanna 0.1 release docs - http://savanna.readthedocs.org/en/0.1/
* Savanna 0.1.1 release docs - http://savanna.readthedocs.org/en/0.1.1/
* Savanna latest (trunk) - http://savanna.readthedocs.org/en/latest/
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
